{"title":"用过Powershell后，我沦陷了","date":"2023-09-24T16:51:46.000Z","source":"_posts/Powershell-is-so-good.md","raw":"---\ntitle: 用过Powershell后，我沦陷了\ndate: 2023-09-24 16:51:46\ntags:\n  - 技术\n---\n\n> 我就是饿死，死外面，从外面跳下去，也不会用 M$ 的垃圾 PowerShell!\n> \n> ……\n> \n> 我草，真香!\n\n<!-- more -->\n\n事情的起因是这样的，作为一般通过Windows用户，突然间我遇到了一个需求：每天ssh登录服务器下载一个备份文件。由于每个备份文件都很大（> 500MB） 我希望我能只在本地保留5份文件。同时，由于网络环境不够可靠，我希望它能自动检测错误并提醒我重试。而我手上只有一个孱弱的 `CMD` \n\n估算了一下我需要的工作量后，我颤颤巍巍地决定尝试一下我从来没用过的 PowerShell。毕竟作为一个后来的产物，比起瞬间启动的bash，启动时间高达 3 秒的它，总不能比 `CMD` 还差吧？\n\n但我还是不太抱希望，因为我脑子里的Bash，一般是语法一般长这样的恐怖东西：\n\n~~（感谢 `husky` 的友情支持）~~\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env sh\nif [ -z \"$husky_skip_init\" ]; then\n  debug () {\n    if [ \"$HUSKY_DEBUG\" = \"1\" ]; then\n      echo \"husky (debug) - $1\"\n    fi\n  }\n\n  readonly hook_name=\"$(basename -- \"$0\")\"\n  debug \"starting $hook_name...\"\n\n  if [ \"$HUSKY\" = \"0\" ]; then\n    debug \"HUSKY env variable is set to 0, skipping hook\"\n    exit 0\n  fi\n\n  if [ -f ~/.huskyrc ]; then\n    debug \"sourcing ~/.huskyrc\"\n    . ~/.huskyrc\n  fi\n\n  readonly husky_skip_init=1\n  export husky_skip_init\n  sh -e \"$0\" \"$@\"\n  exitCode=\"$?\"\n\n  if [ $exitCode != 0 ]; then\n    echo \"husky - $hook_name hook exited with code $exitCode (error)\"\n  fi\n\n  if [ $exitCode = 127 ]; then\n    echo \"husky - command not found in PATH=$PATH\"\n  fi\n\n  exit $exitCode\nfi\n\n```\n\n充满了复杂的变量，充满了对系统的知识，充满了在高级语言看来莫名其妙的语法。语法诡异，需要拓展，这是我对 bash 的刻板印象。本以为， PowerShell 作为写脚本的，也会不免如此，但是我错了。\n\n在Powershell里，我该怎么获取时间？怎么检测错误？怎么做判断？对此一窍不通的我，抱着要啃1MB的文档的心态去打开Powershell的教程，结果却看到：\n\n```powershell\n$file.CreationTime -le (Get-Date).AddDays(-5)\n```\n\n啊？我想象中的管道呢？\n\n`$file` 是一个对象？对象可以直接调用成员函数？啊？`Get-Date`的返回值也是对象？啊？我不用管道了？\n\n在 PowerShell 中，想要删除超过五天前的备份是如此的符合直觉，就像在高级语言中所需要做的那样：\n\n```powershell\n$count = 0\n$backupfiles = Get-ChildItem -Path D:\\Linca\\Backups\n\nforeach ($file in $backupfiles) {\n    if ($file.CreationTime -le (Get-Date).AddDays(-5)) {\n        try {\n            Write-Output \"删除旧备份文件 $file 中……\"\n            Write-Output ''\n            $file.Delete()\n            $count = $count + 1\n        } catch {\n            Write-Output \"删除旧备份文件 $file 时发生了错误 >_<\"\n            Write-Output '-------------------'\n            Write-Output $_\n            Write-Output '-------------------'\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n简简单单，获得了一个文件的Array，非常符合直觉的，遍历这个Array。非常面向对象的，调用 `Delete()` 函数而不是去新建一个进程来 `rm`。甚至出现异常的情况都可以直接 `try-catch`，简直不像脚本语言啊！\n\n真是 太香啦！\n\n附上 [PowerShell Documention](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/)","slug":"Powershell-is-so-good","published":true,"updated":"2024-07-02T01:56:10.264Z","_id":"cly3rcq4y000eciq83kn60g1l","comments":true,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>我就是饿死，死外面，从外面跳下去，也不会用 M$ 的垃圾 PowerShell!</p>\n<p>……</p>\n<p>我草，真香!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>事情的起因是这样的，作为一般通过Windows用户，突然间我遇到了一个需求：每天ssh登录服务器下载一个备份文件。由于每个备份文件都很大（&gt; 500MB） 我希望我能只在本地保留5份文件。同时，由于网络环境不够可靠，我希望它能自动检测错误并提醒我重试。而我手上只有一个孱弱的 <code>CMD</code></p>\n<p>估算了一下我需要的工作量后，我颤颤巍巍地决定尝试一下我从来没用过的 PowerShell。毕竟作为一个后来的产物，比起瞬间启动的bash，启动时间高达 3 秒的它，总不能比 <code>CMD</code> 还差吧？</p>\n<p>但我还是不太抱希望，因为我脑子里的Bash，一般是语法一般长这样的恐怖东西：</p>\n<p><s>（感谢 <code>husky</code> 的友情支持）</s></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#!/usr/bin/env sh</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ -z <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$husky_skip_init</span>&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">debug</span></span> () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$HUSKY_DEBUG</span>&quot;</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;husky (debug) - <span class=\"variable\">$1</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">readonly</span> hook_name=<span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$(basename -- <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$0</span>&quot;</span>)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  debug <span class=\"string\">&quot;starting <span class=\"variable\">$hook_name</span>...&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$HUSKY</span>&quot;</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;0&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    debug <span class=\"string\">&quot;HUSKY env variable is set to 0, skipping hook&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">exit</span> 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ -f ~/.huskyrc ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    debug <span class=\"string\">&quot;sourcing ~/.huskyrc&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    . ~/.huskyrc</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">readonly</span> husky_skip_init=1</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">export</span> husky_skip_init</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sh -e <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$0</span>&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$@</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  exitCode=<span class=\"string\">&quot;$?&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span> != 0 ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;husky - <span class=\"variable\">$hook_name</span> hook exited with code <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span> (error)&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span> = 127 ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;husky - command not found in PATH=<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">exit</span> <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>充满了复杂的变量，充满了对系统的知识，充满了在高级语言看来莫名其妙的语法。语法诡异，需要拓展，这是我对 bash 的刻板印象。本以为， PowerShell 作为写脚本的，也会不免如此，但是我错了。</p>\n<p>在Powershell里，我该怎么获取时间？怎么检测错误？怎么做判断？对此一窍不通的我，抱着要啃1MB的文档的心态去打开Powershell的教程，结果却看到：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$file</span>.CreationTime <span class=\"operator\">-le</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">Get-Date</span>).AddDays(<span class=\"literal\">-5</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>啊？我想象中的管道呢？</p>\n<p><code>$file</code> 是一个对象？对象可以直接调用成员函数？啊？<code>Get-Date</code>的返回值也是对象？啊？我不用管道了？</p>\n<p>在 PowerShell 中，想要删除超过五天前的备份是如此的符合直觉，就像在高级语言中所需要做的那样：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$count</span> = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$backupfiles</span> = <span class=\"built_in\">Get-ChildItem</span> <span class=\"literal\">-Path</span> D:\\Linca\\Backups</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">foreach</span> (<span class=\"variable\">$file</span> <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"variable\">$backupfiles</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"variable\">$file</span>.CreationTime <span class=\"operator\">-le</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">Get-Date</span>).AddDays(<span class=\"literal\">-5</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;删除旧备份文件 <span class=\"variable\">$file</span> 中……&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"variable\">$file</span>.Delete()</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"variable\">$count</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$count</span> + <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">catch</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;删除旧备份文件 <span class=\"variable\">$file</span> 时发生了错误 &gt;_&lt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;-------------------&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"variable\">$_</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;-------------------&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>简简单单，获得了一个文件的Array，非常符合直觉的，遍历这个Array。非常面向对象的，调用 <code>Delete()</code> 函数而不是去新建一个进程来 <code>rm</code>。甚至出现异常的情况都可以直接 <code>try-catch</code>，简直不像脚本语言啊！</p>\n<p>真是 太香啦！</p>\n<p>附上 <a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/\">PowerShell Documention</a></p>\n","excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>我就是饿死，死外面，从外面跳下去，也不会用 M$ 的垃圾 PowerShell!</p>\n<p>……</p>\n<p>我草，真香!</p>\n</blockquote>","more":"<p>事情的起因是这样的，作为一般通过Windows用户，突然间我遇到了一个需求：每天ssh登录服务器下载一个备份文件。由于每个备份文件都很大（&gt; 500MB） 我希望我能只在本地保留5份文件。同时，由于网络环境不够可靠，我希望它能自动检测错误并提醒我重试。而我手上只有一个孱弱的 <code>CMD</code></p>\n<p>估算了一下我需要的工作量后，我颤颤巍巍地决定尝试一下我从来没用过的 PowerShell。毕竟作为一个后来的产物，比起瞬间启动的bash，启动时间高达 3 秒的它，总不能比 <code>CMD</code> 还差吧？</p>\n<p>但我还是不太抱希望，因为我脑子里的Bash，一般是语法一般长这样的恐怖东西：</p>\n<p><s>（感谢 <code>husky</code> 的友情支持）</s></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#!/usr/bin/env sh</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ -z <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$husky_skip_init</span>&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">debug</span></span> () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$HUSKY_DEBUG</span>&quot;</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;husky (debug) - <span class=\"variable\">$1</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">readonly</span> hook_name=<span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$(basename -- <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$0</span>&quot;</span>)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  debug <span class=\"string\">&quot;starting <span class=\"variable\">$hook_name</span>...&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$HUSKY</span>&quot;</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;0&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    debug <span class=\"string\">&quot;HUSKY env variable is set to 0, skipping hook&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">exit</span> 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ -f ~/.huskyrc ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    debug <span class=\"string\">&quot;sourcing ~/.huskyrc&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    . ~/.huskyrc</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">readonly</span> husky_skip_init=1</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">export</span> husky_skip_init</span><br><span class=\"line\">  sh -e <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$0</span>&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"variable\">$@</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  exitCode=<span class=\"string\">&quot;$?&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span> != 0 ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;husky - <span class=\"variable\">$hook_name</span> hook exited with code <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span> (error)&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span> = 127 ]; <span class=\"keyword\">then</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;husky - command not found in PATH=<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">exit</span> <span class=\"variable\">$exitCode</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">fi</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>充满了复杂的变量，充满了对系统的知识，充满了在高级语言看来莫名其妙的语法。语法诡异，需要拓展，这是我对 bash 的刻板印象。本以为， PowerShell 作为写脚本的，也会不免如此，但是我错了。</p>\n<p>在Powershell里，我该怎么获取时间？怎么检测错误？怎么做判断？对此一窍不通的我，抱着要啃1MB的文档的心态去打开Powershell的教程，结果却看到：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$file</span>.CreationTime <span class=\"operator\">-le</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">Get-Date</span>).AddDays(<span class=\"literal\">-5</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>啊？我想象中的管道呢？</p>\n<p><code>$file</code> 是一个对象？对象可以直接调用成员函数？啊？<code>Get-Date</code>的返回值也是对象？啊？我不用管道了？</p>\n<p>在 PowerShell 中，想要删除超过五天前的备份是如此的符合直觉，就像在高级语言中所需要做的那样：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$count</span> = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$backupfiles</span> = <span class=\"built_in\">Get-ChildItem</span> <span class=\"literal\">-Path</span> D:\\Linca\\Backups</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">foreach</span> (<span class=\"variable\">$file</span> <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"variable\">$backupfiles</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"variable\">$file</span>.CreationTime <span class=\"operator\">-le</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">Get-Date</span>).AddDays(<span class=\"literal\">-5</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;删除旧备份文件 <span class=\"variable\">$file</span> 中……&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"variable\">$file</span>.Delete()</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"variable\">$count</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$count</span> + <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">catch</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;删除旧备份文件 <span class=\"variable\">$file</span> 时发生了错误 &gt;_&lt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;-------------------&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"variable\">$_</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">Write-Output</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;-------------------&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>简简单单，获得了一个文件的Array，非常符合直觉的，遍历这个Array。非常面向对象的，调用 <code>Delete()</code> 函数而不是去新建一个进程来 <code>rm</code>。甚至出现异常的情况都可以直接 <code>try-catch</code>，简直不像脚本语言啊！</p>\n<p>真是 太香啦！</p>\n<p>附上 <a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/\">PowerShell Documention</a></p>","path":"2023/09/24/Powershell-is-so-good/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/2023/09/24/Powershell-is-so-good/","tags":[{"name":"技术","_id":"cly3rcq5l001rciq8881j55fu","slug":"技术","path":"tags/技术/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/tags/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/","length":1}],"categories":[],"prev":{"title":"配置Hexo的GitHub Actions自动推送","date":"2023-09-24T19:50:13.000Z","slug":"配置Hexo的自动推送","published":true,"updated":"2024-07-02T01:56:10.268Z","_id":"cly3rcq5j001kciq8bkc16tgi","layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"<p>还在用<code>hexo d</code>来推送你的Blog到Github上吗？本文教您如何使用Github Actions自动推送！</p>","path":"2023/09/24/配置Hexo的自动推送/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/2023/09/24/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEHexo%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81/","__post":true},"next":{"title":"FreeFlarum, 5分钟创建您的独立论坛/个人博客","date":"2023-08-21T18:16:05.000Z","slug":"FreeFlarum-5分钟创建您的独立论坛","published":true,"updated":"2024-07-02T01:56:10.264Z","_id":"cly3rcq4t0006ciq82b256nf7","layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"<p><a href=\"https://freeflarum.com/\">https://freeflarum.com/</a></p>","path":"2023/08/21/FreeFlarum-5分钟创建您的独立论坛/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/2023/08/21/FreeFlarum-5%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%82%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E8%AE%BA%E5%9D%9B/","__post":true},"__post":true}